{"tid":2129016,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前《香港民族論》編輯李啟迪參選 否認投機：政治人物變立場是常見","createTime":"2020-07-28T10:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T16:43:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cea6af5927c86a854c1fee227e5b54ffff97eb2b","tid":2129016,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/GHUCZHYQJT2CZJD2WDMFLKYU4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FGHUCZHYQJT2CZJD2WDMFLKYU4A%2F&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDw3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=5f764c76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FGHUCZHYQJT2CZJD2WDMFLKYU4A%2F&h=5cf0a6be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/GHUCZHYQJT2CZJD2WDMFLKYU4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n曾與梁繼平編撰《香港民族論》的前港大《學苑》編輯李啟迪，加入自由黨田北俊籌組的「希望聯盟」，今天報名於新界東參選，田北俊及周梁淑怡有到場支持。經常被網民譏諷是「政治變色龍」的李啟迪指，政治人物隨時間、環境改變政治立場是常見，不認為自己是「投機」，又稱不擔心被選舉主任DQ，相信所有真誠擁護《基本法》的人會獲得參選資格。田北俊則形容香港現況「變緊形、走緊樣」，指年輕人的行為令北京不滿，北京舉動同樣令港人反感，故他組織聯盟，盼在關鍵時刻「企返香港人呢面」，他讚揚李啟迪的立場由偏激派變「中間」，反問：「一次轉軚係咪一定要批評，係咪應該畀年輕人機會呢？」"},{"pid":"cc5be411a4364efb74c936f61d3088f2e614bd76","tid":2129016,"uid":313584,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"湯家驊 黃成智 狄志遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eedf7ae097494633429463653c8041c1e57ede2","tid":2129016,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:12:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1261a3ba28c8fd68b66e2f53451d91466817f2b","tid":2129016,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc5be411a4364efb74c936f61d3088f2e614bd76","tid":2129016,"uid":313584,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-